WEBVTT

00:01:32.760 --> 00:01:34.200
What've you got in your trunk?

00:01:34.280 --> 00:01:35.159
That smell is awful.

00:01:35.239 --> 00:01:36.159
Fish.

00:01:38.920 --> 00:01:39.760
Been sitting there for weeks.

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:40.799
Yeah, it stinks a bit.

00:01:42.920 --> 00:01:44.400
Your bumper's pretty banged up too.

00:01:44.480 --> 00:01:45.760
Bring it in for repairs sometime.

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:46.920
Alright, thanks for the help.

00:02:23.719 --> 00:02:25.360
Your car's been parked two and a half hours.

00:02:25.479 --> 00:02:26.280
That's another five yuan.

00:02:26.360 --> 00:02:27.520
Look, sir, I only...

00:02:27.599 --> 00:02:29.159
I'm only ten minutes over.

00:02:29.240 --> 00:02:30.840
Could you cut me some slack?

00:02:30.960 --> 00:02:32.439
If I let everyone slide,

00:02:32.520 --> 00:02:34.000
how am I supposed to do my job?

00:02:34.719 --> 00:02:36.319
Besides, it's not up to me.

00:02:36.479 --> 00:02:37.840
Tell you what, do you have a parking voucher?

00:02:38.639 --> 00:02:40.520
My voucher's upstairs.

00:02:40.879 --> 00:02:41.879
Then go get it.

00:02:44.360 --> 00:02:46.240
Who do you think you are?

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:48.319
Hurry it up.

00:02:48.520 --> 00:02:49.599
You're blocking the road.

00:02:51.280 --> 00:02:52.520
Why are you still on the phone?

00:02:53.199 --> 00:02:54.080
If the boss sees this...

00:02:54.080 --> 00:02:55.039
I'm in a meeting.

00:02:55.719 --> 00:02:56.840
Sir, did you hear me?

00:02:57.560 --> 00:02:58.879
Paopao suddenly fainted this afternoon.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:00.039
I'm at the hospital now.

00:03:00.199 --> 00:03:01.080
Come if you can.

00:03:02.400 --> 00:03:03.039
Okay.

00:03:03.240 --> 00:03:04.000
I know.

00:03:04.919 --> 00:03:05.879
Hurry up.

00:03:06.039 --> 00:03:07.479
Why are you still on the phone?

00:03:08.319 --> 00:03:10.199
Alright, stop yelling. I'll scan to pay.

00:03:24.840 --> 00:03:25.680
The doctor suspects

00:03:25.759 --> 00:03:27.319
it might be her hematopoietic system.

00:03:28.039 --> 00:03:29.000
She needs a bone marrow aspiration.

00:03:29.479 --> 00:03:31.719
The county hospital can't do it. We need the provincial one.

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:34.400
Ask your classmate to get us a specialist.

00:03:35.120 --> 00:03:36.520
I'll take a few days off.

00:03:38.919 --> 00:03:39.800
This...

00:03:41.199 --> 00:03:42.719
This... this situation...

00:03:43.439 --> 00:03:45.080
How... how is it so sudden?

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:47.960
Were there any warning signs before?

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:52.199
How could she suddenly...

00:03:52.280 --> 00:03:53.120
Just out of nowhere...

00:03:53.960 --> 00:03:55.360
Let's just get the tests done first.

00:04:15.319 --> 00:04:16.120
Attorney Luo.

00:04:16.839 --> 00:04:19.399
Attorney Feng's waiting for you in the meeting room.

00:04:44.680 --> 00:04:45.399
Luo.

00:04:46.519 --> 00:04:47.240
Luo.

00:04:49.720 --> 00:04:50.680
Sit down, let's talk.

00:04:53.199 --> 00:04:54.879
The firm has decided

00:04:55.120 --> 00:04:56.240
to make some

00:04:56.240 --> 00:04:57.439
position adjustments for certain attorneys.

00:04:57.879 --> 00:04:59.680
You're always busy anyway, aren't you?

00:04:59.839 --> 00:05:00.480
Right?

00:05:01.199 --> 00:05:01.959
Take a look first.

00:05:02.120 --> 00:05:03.920
If there's any issue, come to me.

00:05:05.120 --> 00:05:05.800
Okay?

00:05:07.399 --> 00:05:08.120
Come on, sit.

00:05:15.959 --> 00:05:17.480
What... what does this mean?

00:05:17.879 --> 00:05:19.439
Are you firing me?

00:05:20.199 --> 00:05:21.040
Why?

00:05:21.720 --> 00:05:23.680
If... if you want to fire me,

00:05:23.759 --> 00:05:24.560
you should at least give me

00:05:24.560 --> 00:05:26.560
a reasonable, legitimate reason, right?

00:05:27.199 --> 00:05:28.959
I've been here for seven years.

00:05:29.279 --> 00:05:30.160
Seven years!

00:05:30.319 --> 00:05:31.439
All the hard, dirty work,

00:05:31.519 --> 00:05:32.319
the stuff nobody else wanted to do,

00:05:32.399 --> 00:05:33.360
all got dumped on me.

00:05:33.480 --> 00:05:35.000
A big chunk of the firm's income

00:05:35.079 --> 00:05:37.120
came from the shady deals I did for Feng Mao.

00:05:37.240 --> 00:05:38.480
And now you just fire me, just like that?

00:05:38.480 --> 00:05:39.720
You can't just use me and throw me away.

00:05:39.720 --> 00:05:40.399
I'm telling you...

00:05:40.480 --> 00:05:42.160
Don't get so worked up, alright?

00:05:42.720 --> 00:05:44.920
This wasn't decided by just the two of us.

00:05:45.480 --> 00:05:46.959
How am I supposed to stay calm?

00:05:47.040 --> 00:05:48.439
Stop shifting the blame.

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:49.279
Let me tell you.

00:05:49.399 --> 00:05:50.920
For seven years, all the time I should've spent at home,

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:51.959
I poured into this place.

00:05:52.079 --> 00:05:53.199
And now you give me this?

00:05:53.279 --> 00:05:54.199
How am I supposed to accept this?

00:05:54.199 --> 00:05:55.839
Luo Xiao, you really don't know what's good for you, do you?

00:05:57.040 --> 00:05:58.240
You think you've done more than me?

00:06:00.040 --> 00:06:01.000
Let me tell you,

00:06:02.160 --> 00:06:03.240
there's nothing wrong with you.

00:06:04.399 --> 00:06:06.279
Not a single thing.

00:06:06.680 --> 00:06:07.839
You're just not important anymore.

00:06:07.920 --> 00:06:09.839
The firm doesn't need you. Get it?

00:06:11.199 --> 00:06:12.480
You've got two options.

00:06:13.360 --> 00:06:14.519
Take the money and get lost,

00:06:14.720 --> 00:06:15.759
or we go down together,

00:06:15.839 --> 00:06:17.120
fight to the bitter end.

00:06:18.759 --> 00:06:19.560
Your choice.

00:06:38.240 --> 00:06:40.120
You've been parked here for five hours this time.

00:06:40.639 --> 00:06:42.360
Your last parking voucher expired.

00:06:42.600 --> 00:06:44.639
Go get a new one for this month.

00:07:09.920 --> 00:07:11.199
I told him

00:07:11.319 --> 00:07:12.600
to park further back.

00:07:13.079 --> 00:07:14.360
But you just had to let him block the way.

00:07:21.680 --> 00:07:23.079
Are you out of your mind, kid?

00:07:23.279 --> 00:07:24.439
Don't you know the rules?

00:07:24.680 --> 00:07:26.199
Absolutely outrageous.

00:07:26.800 --> 00:07:28.319
How did your parents raise you?

00:07:30.639 --> 00:07:32.000
I'm reporting you!

00:07:45.680 --> 00:07:47.040
Whatever you had to pay today,

00:07:47.040 --> 00:07:48.399
we both have an idea.

00:07:50.199 --> 00:07:51.199
Just in case...

00:07:53.319 --> 00:07:55.560
I mean, in case Paopao needs money,

00:07:56.600 --> 00:07:57.920
we should both be prepared.

00:08:00.160 --> 00:08:01.120
How about this:

00:08:02.199 --> 00:08:03.560
you and Paopao head over first.

00:08:04.480 --> 00:08:06.000
I'll figure something out here.

00:08:06.360 --> 00:08:07.879
Message me if anything comes up.

00:08:08.120 --> 00:08:09.040
I'll come right away.

00:08:11.959 --> 00:08:13.040
You haven't eaten yet, have you?

00:08:17.319 --> 00:08:18.120
It's been hard on you.

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:35.200
This checkup,

00:08:35.879 --> 00:08:37.159
whether Paopao's okay or not,

00:08:37.279 --> 00:08:38.519
I want a divorce either way.

00:08:43.440 --> 00:08:45.840
Can we wait till Paopao gets better

00:08:46.320 --> 00:08:47.399
before we talk about this?

00:08:48.440 --> 00:08:49.720
We don't have to tell Paopao,

00:08:49.799 --> 00:08:51.039
but I can't keep waiting forever.

00:08:54.639 --> 00:08:55.600
I know.

00:08:57.480 --> 00:08:58.519
I know.

00:08:59.960 --> 00:09:01.039
I've held you back.

00:09:01.399 --> 00:09:03.240
You want to hurry and find someone better.

00:09:05.559 --> 00:09:07.559
Luo Xiao, can you stop acting crazy?

00:09:09.519 --> 00:09:10.759
I just feel like...

00:09:13.120 --> 00:09:14.240
I've tried my best,

00:09:16.279 --> 00:09:17.759
but it's just not working.

00:09:18.519 --> 00:09:19.919
I mean, this house,

00:09:20.600 --> 00:09:21.440
the car,

00:09:22.120 --> 00:09:24.039
the life right in front of you,

00:09:24.799 --> 00:09:25.759
that's all you care about.

00:09:25.840 --> 00:09:28.159
Luo Xiao, can we not talk about this?

00:09:28.879 --> 00:09:31.200
It's my fault, I'm the problem, okay?

00:09:31.519 --> 00:09:32.919
I just can't live like this anymore.

00:09:40.080 --> 00:09:41.200
Get yourself a bowl.

00:10:20.720 --> 00:10:22.279
Is this where Bro Mao

00:10:23.080 --> 00:10:24.759
hides his stuff?

00:10:59.559 --> 00:11:00.840
Hello, Greenfield Cemetery.

00:11:00.919 --> 00:11:03.120
Choose with care, rest in peace.

00:11:03.360 --> 00:11:04.960
How may I help you?

00:11:13.039 --> 00:11:13.759
What about this one?

00:11:14.480 --> 00:11:15.200
Okay.

00:11:19.120 --> 00:11:20.720
Something's up at the firm, I'm heading out.

00:11:20.840 --> 00:11:21.840
Not getting dressed?

00:11:51.519 --> 00:11:52.360
What are you doing here?

00:11:55.679 --> 00:11:56.440
Sir,

00:11:57.200 --> 00:11:57.960
well,

00:11:58.480 --> 00:12:00.480
I'm here to take care of something for Bro Mao.

00:12:00.600 --> 00:12:01.440
Bro Mao?

00:12:06.240 --> 00:12:07.639
Hold on, I'll open the door.

00:12:10.799 --> 00:12:12.120
Car's still parked up there.

00:12:12.320 --> 00:12:13.279
Jackpot.

00:13:57.679 --> 00:13:59.159
Scared you, didn't I, buddy?

00:14:00.120 --> 00:14:01.960
By the time you hear this recording,

00:14:04.679 --> 00:14:05.679
I'll already be dead.

00:14:08.360 --> 00:14:10.919
Us brothers meeting up, it's fate.

00:14:12.279 --> 00:14:13.320
Thank you

00:14:14.200 --> 00:14:15.720
for coming to my funeral.

00:14:17.000 --> 00:14:17.919
No matter

00:14:18.320 --> 00:14:19.440
what happened before I died,

00:14:19.639 --> 00:14:20.600
or what grudges we had,

00:14:21.879 --> 00:14:22.720
I hope

00:14:23.120 --> 00:14:24.200
from now on,

00:14:25.120 --> 00:14:26.360
we can be happy

00:14:27.480 --> 00:14:28.960
and let bygones be bygones with a smile.

00:14:31.039 --> 00:14:33.480
Isn't there a song that goes like that?

00:14:34.919 --> 00:14:37.480
Give your brother a hug,

00:14:38.080 --> 00:14:39.840
and share what's in your heart.

00:14:40.919 --> 00:14:41.919
So, you know,

00:14:42.559 --> 00:14:43.440
my friends...